Description:
    Integrates the error notification service "Airbrake".

Example:
    `rails generate cms:component:airbrake`
    `rails generate cms:component:airbrake --skip_deployment_notification`

    Gems: airbrake
    Configuration: extends config/custom_cloud.yml
    Initializer: config/initializers/airbrake.rb
    Deployment: extends deploy/after_restart.rb